text: Beautifully updated RAMBLER on 2.8 ACRES with a detached 28'X30' SHOP and 14'X20' CARPORT! Located on Fir Island and surrounded by VIEWS of water, mountains and farmland! This 3-bedroom, 2-bath home features an updated kitchen with quartz countertops, tile backsplash and SS appliances. Open floor plan with 2 living spaces; one with wood stove, large dining room and tastefully renovated bathrooms. Newer windows, interior paint and trim and luxury vinyl plank floors throughout. Fully fenced property with secure access gate and covered back deck perfect for entertaining! New septic system, HEAT PUMP and lots of RV parking! Come enjoy the beauty of the Skagit Valley! One-year home WARRANTY included!

Fully remodeled from top to bottom, this stunning home is ready for you! Enjoy peace of mind with a new roof, new siding, and a new water heaterjust to name a few updates. The inviting living room features a cozy wood-burning fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings. With its east-facing orientation and large windows, natural light floods the living spaces, creating a bright and welcoming atmosphere. This home combines modern updates with timeless charm, offering comfort and style. Dont miss outschedule your showing today!

A rare find: the perfect house and shop combo in a prime central location! This charming property offers open-concept living with vaulted ceilings, quality oak cabinetry, and a built-in island bar ideal for morning coffee. The thoughtful layout separates the bedrooms for added privacy, plus theres a versatile office or 3rd bedroom. The star of the show is the XL heated 4-bay shop with RV-height clearance, extra storage, and a man doorperfect for hobbies, a workshop, or storing all your toys. Enjoy mature landscaping with gorgeous roses, wisteria, lilacs, rhubarb, strawberries, tomatoes, and blueberries. An asphalt courtyard provides ample parking behind the shop, while two covered patios offer peaceful spaces to relax and unwind.

Welcome to this beautiful 900 sq. ft. home featuring a spacious loft and stunning custom finishes of Pine Tongue and Groove cathedral ceilings, granite countertops, and an elegant tile bathroom floor. Enjoy year-round comfort with an energy-efficient ductless heat pump and an EPA-approved Soapstone wood stove. The property boasts a propane range, hot water, and a Leaf guard gutter system with a lifetime warranty, along with a 22x24 carport. With a foundation allowing for a daylight basement with outdoor access, and proximity to the Scenic Skagit River and numerous parks, this home offers both comfort and convenience. A gardeners dream with a new garden and fruit trees creating a serene atmosphere.

Nestled in the heart of Anacortes, this charming rambler boasts spectacular Water & Mountain views from the cozy interior & spacious front yard. Located on an oversized Corner Lot in a picturesque neighborhood, the property includes a large shop/detached garage, perfect for storage or projects. Inside, be greeted by a warm & inviting space, recently updated with stylish Laminate flooring in the living areas, plush Carpets in the bedrooms & modern tile in the bathrooms. The kitchen shines w/ newer Cabinets, Quartz Countertops & a sleek backsplash, while updated bathroom vanities & fixtures add a contemporary feel. 2 oversized covered patios for entertainment! Ample parking for cars, RV/ boat. Just moments from Old Town, schools & shopping.

This stunning contemporary home is nestled in a park-like setting in the sought-after Cedar Ridge neighborhood with private lake access to Sixteen lake. This 4 bed 3 bath gem boasts a formal dining room and den, storage under the stairs, spacious living room with appx 20ft ceilings.Gourmet kitchen complete with plenty of cabinet & counter space, gas range & stainless steel appliances. The walk-in pantry provides ample storage space for all your cooking essentials.Convenient 2nd floor laundry, The primary bedroom is a true oasis, featuring a cozy seating area that can also double as an office space.2 car garage with lots of built-ins. Outside you'll be greeted with mature and meticulous landscaping, large shed to store all of your lawn tools.

Lifestyle HOUSE - Fresh updated Rambler with Washington Park as your backyard! Ideally located in a quiet residential neighborhood on east facing lot. Just finished remodeling including Interior paint, Laminate plank flooring, new beautiful bathroom vanities & lighting! Great use of space with the Spacious Primary suite on one side & 2 additional bedrooms on the other side of the house. Fully fenced-in private rear yard and second driveway with room to park your RV/boat. All this is with Skyline amenities including 2 clubhouses, pickleball court(s), Basketball court(s), private waterfront park, playgrounds AND Washington Park in your backyard!

Discover comfort and tranquility at 3907 Copper Pond. This well maintained home offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and 1820 sq. ft. of living space, providing ample room for everyone. Enjoy sun-filled interiors, and spacious bedrooms. With top-rated schools and convenient access to amenities, this is the perfect retreat!

Charming, well-maintained cottage on a corner lot, the largest lot in the neighborhood! This home features a welcoming covered front porch & beautiful Pergo wood flooring throughout. The living/dining area features a vaulted ceiling, creating a spacious atmosphere. The kitchen shines with new stainless steel appliances, including a gas range. The primary bedroom is generously sized w/double closets for ample storage, while the main bathroom features a modern, low-profile walk-in shower. Relax on the TimberTech deck with low-rise stairs. Additional upgrades include a high-efficiency gas furnace & hot water tank plus a half bath was added in the laundry room. The HOA dues cover, lawn, garage & common area maintenance.

This stunning rambler in Jacobs Meadow is a true gem! Featuring a chefs dream kitchen with granite countertops, ample storage, and stainless steel appliances, its perfect for culinary enthusiasts. The home offers 3 spacious bedrooms plus a dedicated office, ideal for remote work or study. The well-appointed primary suite includes a walk-in closet, dual vanities, and a beautifully tiled shower. Step outside to the covered deck, which overlooks a fenced backyard and picturesque meadow teeming with wildlife. Located in a welcoming neighborhood with charming, walkable roads and sidewalks, this home combines comfort and convenience beautifully.

Welcome to your dream home in the Arbor Glen community. This beautifully designed 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence boasts 1, 520 square feet of modern living space. Enjoy a spacious floor plan featuring an inviting living room, gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, a stylish tile backsplash, and Aristocraft soft-close cabinetry. The luxurious primary suite offers a private retreat, while the convenient upstairs laundry adds practicality. With an easy care yard and a 1-car garage, this home perfectly combines comfort and convenience. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity!

Rare find on Bow Hill! This gorgeous custom-built rambler is in a gated community on 6.2 acres w/2 beautifully landscaped. Great floor plan w/no wasted space & lots of natural light. Stunning kitchen with cream cabinets, hardwood floors, SS appls., large island, & dream walk-in pantry. Great room has gas fireplace & French doors to a large, partially covered deck. Office w/built-ins & window seat. Spacious dining room off kitchen and cozy living room. Generous primary has walk-in closet, bath w/split vanities, shower & soaking tub. Enjoy coffee on the covered front porch. XL 3-car attached garage with cabinets, plus a 30x40 3-bay (1 tall door for RV) shop that is insulated, with power & water. County living, but only 1 mile from freeway!

Location, location! This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is perfectly situated on a spacious corner lot across the street from multiple sports fields & Volunteer Park. This home has all new interior paint, carpet & a newer roof making it move in ready. Finished garage space has been transformed into a versatile flex space, ideal for a home gym, game room, or any large scale activity or remove the wall and take it back to a 2 car garage. The kitchen boasts a large restaurant style gas range that invites you to explore your culinary creativity. Large partially fenced yard is a great space for outdoor activities, includes a large storage shed & plenty of extra parking. With endless potential & unbeatable location, this home is ready for you!

This spacious home in Digby Heights is a dream for entertaining! Beautiful laminate wood floors and wood trim are featured throughout the main floor, offering a bedroom/office space, a 1/2 bath, large living room, gourmet kitchen with granite tile countertops and breakfast area. A butler's pantry sits off the formal dining room, with wet bar, mini fridge and wine fridge. Upstairs you'll find a gigantic bonus room ideal for a rec room or home theater, a full bath, laundry room. There are 3 large bedrooms upstairs, in addition to a luxurious primary suite boasting soaring ceilings, huge dual walk-in closets and 5 piece bathroom. Add in a covered patio with gas fireplace and a fenced yard, and there is room for everybody to spread out!
nearby_schools: Mount Vernon School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Discover a rare opportunity with this charming 1946-built, 4-bedroom, 2-bath home, hitting the market for the first time! Nestled on a peaceful 0.48-acre lot in Bow, WA, this 1, 898 sq. ft. home combines classic character with stunning views of Puget Sound. The 948 sq. ft. partially finished basement offers plenty of storage or potential for additional living space. Enjoy the spacious front and backyard, perfect for relaxing or entertaining in a serene, rural setting. Located in scenic Skagit County, this property offers the best of both worlds tranquil living surrounded by natural beauty, yet just a short drive to nearby amenities. Don't miss this chance to own a piece of Pacific Northwest paradise!

Great home for a first-time buyer, or investor looking for a rental property. Situated on nearly a quarter-acre corner lot, this home features a nice-sized single-car detached garage that can double as a workshop, with ample room outside for parking or an RV. Enjoy the convenience of being near local parks, the river, downtown, and I-5! This home is sold as-is, offering endless potential to customize and update to suit your style. Dont miss out on this fantastic opportunity!

Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Bay Hill neighborhood of Burlington! This beautifully updated residence combines modern sophistication with timeless charm, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. You walk into the sitting room on the right and dining on the left. The Chef's kitchen is open to your living room. Three spacious bedrooms including the full primary suite. There's plenty of room for your projects in the 3 car garage. The beautifully landscaped backyard is perfect for outdoor entertaining. A spacious deck with a gazebo overlooks the private fenced-in yard and Koi pond providing a serene space for summer barbecues or simply unwinding after a long day. Make this your Next Home.

Bring your dreams to life on this private and secluded 20 acre parcel just 10 minutes from town at the end of a dirt road. Enjoy the sounds of Walker Creek running through the property, and the abundant wildlife in your backyard.There could be some marketable timber. No well allowed, will need a water catchment system.

Welcome to this brand new 4-bedroom manufactured home, perfectly situated on a spacious half-acre lot in the serene Cape Horn community in Concrete. Featuring a new septic system for 3 bedrooms, this home also includes a versatile bonus room with endless potentialwhether you imagine a large walk-in pantry, home office, canning room, or crafting space. Enjoy the peaceful, quiet life here and the comfort of knowing youre in a brand-new home with modern amenities. HOA fee includes water bill, only $27/mo! Be sure to check out the floor plan in the photos. Interest rate buy down available with our preferred lender.

Experience the perfect blend for an active or relaxed lifestyle in this Skyline community of Anacortes. Whether you are looking to downsize, a second home, or a full-time residence, this rambler offers versatility for any lifestyle. Youll find 1, 992 sf, 3 beds, 1.75 baths, an office, bonus room, vaulted ceilings in the great room and the owners suite includes a private bath & sitting area. Situated on a corner lot next to a creek, the property features territorial views, parking for 8 vehicles, & room for an RV or boat. Community amenities include a clubhouse, cabana, tennis & pickleball courts, parks, beach access & RV spaces. Minutes to Skyline Marina, beaches, Washington Park and Sugarloaf Mountain. Easy commute by boat to San Juans

Perfect starter or investment home in Sedro-Woolley! This 2 bedroom 1 bath home offers just over 800 sq ft of living space including a large living room and remodeled kitchen with updated cabinets, counters and tile backsplash. Kitchen appliances all stay. Mostly fenced and level backyard is great for entertaining and the home also has covered carport parking off of the alley. This may be the opportunity to enter the housing market or expand your investment property portfolio that you've been looking for!

Discover the charm of small-town living with this brand-new 3-bedroom, 1.75-bathroom Energy Star home, complete with an attached garage on a fully paved, private cul-de-sac. With no HOA and over $26, 000 in upgrades, this home is thoughtfully designed and built to last. It features a full slab foundation, cement block crawlspace, and a rambler-style layout that maximizes space and natural light. The open-concept kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, a full tile backsplash, a large island with bar seating, and plenty of storage. The master suite offers a walk-in closet and an elegant, tiled shower. Outside, the low-maintenance yard, with new sod and fencing, is ready for you to make it your own.
